query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.projectTypeId, pt.name as project_type_name, 
(SELECT COUNT(*) FROM milestone_templates WHERE projectTypeId = p.projectTypeId AND isActive = 1) as template_count
FROM projects p 
JOIN project_types pt ON p.projectTypeId = pt.id 
WHERE p.name LIKE '%prueba comercial%'
